c: 35
v: 45
t: "walaw yeaqb allah alnaas bima eamiluu min aldhunub walmeasy ma tarak ealaa zahr al'ard min dabat tadibb elyha, wlkn yumhlhm wywkhr eqabhm 'iilaa waqt maelum endh, fa'iidha ja' waqt eqabhm fa'iina allah kan bieibadih bsyrana, la yakhfaa ealayh 'ahad mnhm, wala yaezub eanh eilm shay' min amwrhm, wsyjazyhm bima eamiluu min khayr 'aw shr"